    "created_at": "2015-09-21T03:28:58Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-21T03:28:58Z",
    "body": "Indeed, however by merely using `setContextMenu`, [the primary click action is no longer configurable](https://github.com/atom/electron/blob/e4a7352b6299a03a42f545cfec1c45dde60bac41/atom/browser/ui/tray_icon_cocoa.mm#L210-L216):\n\n``` objc\n- (void)mouseUp:(NSEvent*)event {\n  // ... snip ...\n  // Show menu when single clicked on the icon.\n  if (event.clickCount == 1 && menuController_)\n    [statusItem_ popUpStatusItemMenu:[menuController_ menu]];\n\n  // Don't emit click events when menu is showing.\n  if (menuController_)\n    return;\n  // ... snip ...\n}\n```\n"
  },
